  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Supervisor",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Assist the Project Manager or Site Manager in planning and managing daily site activities.</p></li><li><p>Supervise works carried out by subcontractors and in-house teams to ensure smooth site operations.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate closely with engineers, supervisors, and other site personnel to meet project timelines and milestones.</p></li><li><p>Ensure installations are executed in accordance with approved drawings, technical specifications, and method statements.</p></li><li><p>Monitor work progress, workmanship quality, and compliance with project standards.</p></li><li><p>Enforce proper work practices and ensure rectification of defects when required.</p></li><li><p>Conduct and lead daily toolbox meetings, delivering clear work instructions and safety briefings.</p></li></ul>",
